  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span>\n   <br></p>\n  <div data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-bottom: 0px; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px; color: rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__0\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"caret-color:rgb(34, 34, 34);font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(163, 163, 163) !important;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-shadow:transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:27.2px;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n    <div mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__2\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n     <div data-id=\"85660\" data-custom=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" data-color=\"rgb(117, 117, 118)\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__3\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n      <div data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: 2em; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.5em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-style: none; border-left-style: none; text-decoration: inherit; visibility: visible; line-height: 27.2px;\" mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"27.200000762939453\" class=\"js_darkmode__4\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 2em 0px 0px;padding: 0.5em 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);border-top: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;border-right-style: none;border-left-style: none;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;line-height: 27.2px;\">\n       <p mp-original-font-size=\"17\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" data-style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; margin-top: -1.2em; outline: 0px; text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px; text-align: center; font-family: inherit; border-width: initial; border-style: initial; border-color: currentcolor; visibility: visible; line-height: 29.75px;\" class=\"js_darkmode__5\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-shadow: transparent 0px 0px 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 0px 0px 0px;text-align: center;font-family: inherit;border-width: initial;border-style: initial;border-color: currentcolor;visibility: visible;line-height: 29.75px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span mp-original-font-size=\"15\" mp-original-line-height=\"29.75\" style=\"padding:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:15px;line-height:29.75px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;background-color:rgb(117, 117, 118);outline:0px;max-width:100%;margin-top:0px;font-family:inherit;margin-bottom:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">机器之心报道</span></span></p>\n       <p style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;clear: both;min-height: 1em;text-align: center;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.6em;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 12px;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">编辑：冷猫、</span><span leaf=\"\">+0</span></strong></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <blockquote style=\"visibility: visible;\">\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible;\">打造科研界的 AlphaGo。</span></p>\n   <span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;AFXndTDLsoiLQkxp65Dcwlurnqd&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;打造科研界的AlphaGo&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+d&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7523040276240252947&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:false,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;996ba5e9-d732-411c-a343-ae20a3feb66c&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:12,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:21,&quot;end&quot;:34},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;AEUkdROSroys5AxxyIzcEWlonOe&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，理论物理学家、物理学新视野奖获得者 Alex Lupsasca 有了一个新身份：OpenAI for Science 团队的首位学术研究员。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512401\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5357142857142857\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"924\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=de8a49fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadLEF4YazPUz58q4fEtZhVuyR9dYribU6QXhTHOQibFbTNSIMyuZ7AUDoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他所加入的，正是 OpenAI 在今年 9 月由其首席产品官（CPO）Kevin Weil 宣布开启的一项雄心勃勃的新计划：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">打造一个 AI 驱动的平台，以加速人类的科学发现进程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512402\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7363057324840764\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"785\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3232ebed&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iad3elAdb4nTFH92Fa62iaaEKibUnia6ic7bcLTlrKibHibiapM0pz5OVA5OOLng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Alex Lupsasca 表示，他曾长期认为 AI 无法触及研究前沿，但是 GPT-5 Pro 的出现改变了他的想法。 GPT-5 Pro 在不到 30 分钟内，就独立推导出了他本人花费数天艰苦计算才找到的黑洞扰动理论中的一个全新对称性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512403\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2445414847161572\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"916\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9c4d6922&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadZuu6At2bKjHMdTQ0U2SqicAlCLdvqF9Qo1WPLSpbeQHLMTNmPKYBgiaw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">事情要从他于今年 6 月发表的一篇关于黑洞物理学的论文说起。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512408\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.1787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bd5c75b5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadNW9G84OCFDKFkBJsOEXF5HT5s76WTuwF43qKUhfdLhdjybhS93qbdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">论文地址：<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.05298\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2506.05298</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在这篇论文中，Lupsasca 提出了一个关于静态、轴对称克尔黑洞扰动的新共形对称性。简单来说，他发现了一种描述黑洞行为的「隐藏」规则。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一发现的重要推论是，黑洞没有潮汐形变能力，即它们的「勒夫数」为零，这对于引力波天文学等领域具有重要意义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Lupsasca 本人表示，一旦这些对称性被知晓，要揭示其物理意义相对容易，但「最困难的部分是找到它们精确的数学形式（甚至确定它们是否存在）」。他表示，这个过程花费了他「数天时间的艰苦计算」，其结果的复杂性从论文中的公式就可见一斑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512404\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.5136612021857924\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"915\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5f00edb5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iad3wc1a3D2fyQPiah7rYJG84icCE8meL3TzHw9YLlxsj71fLmKtfGBVW4Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">GPT-5 Pro 发布后，Lupsasca 抱着试一试的心态，将同样的问题抛给了它。结果令他「极度震惊」：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">GPT-5 Pro 在不到 30 分钟内就重新发现了这一结果。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">对话链接：<a href=\"https://chatgpt.com/share/68b006eb-ee0c-8005-903f-bf92065d7e03\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatgpt.com/share/68b006eb-ee0c-8005-903f-bf92065d7e03</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Lupsasca 对 GPT-5 Pro 的快速回应产生了怀疑，便询问了 GPT 是否从网上寻求相关答案，但 GPT-5 Pro 在 9 分 16 秒的推理后否认，并再次给出了推理过程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512405\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.22777777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e02eccaf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadf0E54a73E6oy79danqYqEJFLic55oYibBENpnxLbARpOYAMOOtjEe2Hg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Lupsasca 补充说，AI 的表现并非完美无瑕。在解决这个完整问题之前，需要先用一个更简单的「平直时空」案例对其进行「预热」。尽管如此，他认为这仍然是一次「令人难以置信的飞跃」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">并且，GPT-5 Pro 的能力不仅限于理论推导。Lupsasca 还发现，它同样能处理观测天体物理学中的难题，生成的答案质量堪比一名优秀的研究生花费数天时间进行研究所得出的结论。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512406\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.24721878862793573\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"809\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ec8ea5bb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadRZkGmhQ6smJ73kwGQuMSEN5w5JYLHg7NibMic6p7iboslE0TJba2JpcCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\">对话链接：<a href=\"https://chatgpt.com/share/68d154c9-5618-8005-80b9-7e5ac0827b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatgpt.com/share/68d154c9-5618-8005-80b9-7e5ac0827b76</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">OpenAI 首席研究员 Mark Chen 在为 Lupsasca 加入 OpenAI for Science 团队表示激动之余，也关注到了 GPT-5 在短时间内重现黑洞物理研究的表现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他激动地表示，这不亚于 2016 年 AlphaGo 与李世石的对决中，AlphaGo 第 37 步的「神之一手」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512407\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8351851851851851\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a7a4c1d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadbaGVkBCiaEJ73ibQXjJsjUpESO4twMq0PI2vdphWhekzSYVKpSLwKicMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如今，人工智能和自然科学的联系愈发紧密。自然科学，尤其是物理学中的一些概念和理论，对人工智能领域的一些架构设计产生了深刻的影响。「学物理的不准转计算机」不仅是一个梗，更是学科领域融合的最佳体现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">很快，AI 也会在各大学术研究领域有更深的影响力，科研领域的 AlphaGo 时刻正越来越近。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">想要建造最大黑洞望远镜的科学家</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503512398\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9890196078431372\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1275\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0f29610b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW8ETJmEkGIXiaw76xqtT01iadckicNMstbgMGy8uE7Q8JG0b2KUQAVkibzZCgqGzK0NZTN0mthMpaOQOg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Alex Lupsasca 是一位著名理论物理学家，研究方向包括黑洞、经典与量子引力以及相对论天体物理，自 2022 年起担任范德堡大学物理与数学系的助理教授。在此之前曾在哈佛大学和普林斯顿大学任职。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">他与 Michael Johnson 共同获得了突破奖基金会颁发的 2024 年「物理学新视野奖」，并因我在黑洞成像方面的工作，获国际广义相对论与引力学会颁发的 2024 年 IUPAP 广义相对论与引力量子基金会青年科学家奖。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">目前，Alex Lupsasca 是「黑洞探测者（Black Hole Explorer，BHEX）」项目的首席科学家，该项目计划发射一颗环绕地球轨道的卫星，以获取天文学史上最清晰的图像。BHEX 的目标是直接观测黑洞事件视界尺度的结构，并测量绕黑洞运行的「光子环」，准备申报为下一代 NASA Small Explorers 任务，预计于 2032 年发射。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: normal;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://chatgpt.com/share/68b006eb-ee0c-8005-903f-bf92065d7e03\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatgpt.com/share/68b006eb-ee0c-8005-903f-bf92065d7e03</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://chatgpt.com/share/68d154c9-5618-8005-80b9-7e5ac0827b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://chatgpt.com/share/68d154c9-5618-8005-80b9-7e5ac0827b76</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://lupsasca.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lupsasca.com/</a></span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mgu84xpu-rqqzzk\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">#bio</span></a></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\"><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/709590684\" target=\"_blank\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/709590684</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "GPT-5 Pro 在半小时内重现黑洞物理学复杂推导，促使黑洞物理学家 Alex Lupsasca 加盟 OpenAI，加速科学发现。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "GPT-5 Pro 在半小时内重现黑洞物理学复杂推导，促使黑洞物理学家 Alex Lupsasca 加盟 OpenAI，加速科学发现。",
